description: Spacious top floor home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms beautifully renovated in 2020. Primary bedroom with en-suite full bathroom and walk in closet is located at the front of the property. 2 spacious bedrooms and full guest bathroom in the middle section. The rear of the home is a wide open kitchen/living room which walks out to a private rear deck. Tall ceilings and lots of natural light in this home. Welcoming entry featuring exposed brick hallway at the entry. Excellent closets, central AC, electric fireplace, in unit laundry and hardwood floors throughout. Top level of a two unit condo association. Owner occupied building and a beautiful place to claim as your next home.
